---
title: Greek-Style Chicken Bowl  with Veggie-Loaded Rice & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Chicken and veggies can get a little tiresome, but we bet with this new twist, everyone at the table will be wanting a second
helping. With flavours of garlic, a cooling yoghurt dolloped on top of an array of veggies and rice, it can be confirmed that
beef and veggies are back in the good books!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

